(other issues \(and I don't know if they can do partial updates or have to re-render the entire) Tj
T*
(new buffer\). In the old days, the idea of having two buffers for your program's window was a) Tj
T*
(decided luxury. You might not even have one buffer and instead be drawing directly onto screen) Tj
T*
(memory. I'll call this repaint mode , because you directly repainted some or all of your window) Tj
